text: Ivana Ivaštanin (born 7 August 1996) is a Montenegrin footballer who plays as a defender. She has been a member of the Montenegro women's national team. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Montenegrin women's footballers Category:Montenegro women's international footballers Category:ŽFK Ekonomist players
